msgid ""
"Full control within assigned teams — players, evaluations, activities, "
"goals, and team settings. Scoped to team."
msgstr ""
"Volledige controle binnen toegewezen teams — spelers, evaluaties, "
"activiteiten, doelen en teaminstellingen. Beperkt tot team."

