msgid ""
"Evaluate and observe within assigned teams. Can create and edit own "
"evaluations; cannot edit other coaches' evaluations. Scoped to team."
msgstr ""
"Evalueer en observeer binnen toegewezen teams. Kan eigen evaluaties aanmaken "
"en bewerken; kan evaluaties van andere trainers niet bewerken. Beperkt tot "
"team."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:466
