"surfaces."
msgstr ""
"v1.5: Teams, People, Players, Trial_Cases, Sessions (activiteiten), "
"Session_Attendance, Evaluations, Evaluation_Ratings, Goals, Player_Journey. "
"Referentie-tabbladen (Eval_Categories, Category_Weights, _Lookups) zijn "
"alleen ter documentatie — beheer die via de bestaande Configuratie-schermen."

