#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:364
msgid ""
"Master data — uncheck to use the rows already in your club instead of "
"generating new ones. These three toggles only apply to the procedural source "
"(Excel + hybrid read master data from the workbook regardless)."
msgstr ""
"Master-data — uitvinken om de bestaande rijen in je club te gebruiken in "
"plaats van nieuwe te genereren. Deze drie schakelaars gelden alleen voor de "
"procedurele bron (Excel + hybride lezen master-data sowieso uit het "
"werkboek)."

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:368
msgid "Generate teams"
msgstr "Ploegen genereren"

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:369
msgid "uncheck to use existing teams in the club."
msgstr "uitvinken om bestaande ploegen in de club te gebruiken."

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:373
msgid "Generate people + WP users"
msgstr "Mensen + WP-gebruikers genereren"

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:374
msgid ""
"uncheck to skip the 36-account creation. Existing People rows + their WP "
"users stay untouched."
msgstr ""
"uitvinken om de 36-account-creatie over te slaan. Bestaande Mensen-rijen en "
"hun WP-gebruikers blijven onaangeraakt."

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:378
msgid "Generate players"
msgstr "Spelers genereren"

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:379
msgid "uncheck to use existing players in the club."
msgstr "uitvinken om bestaande spelers in de club te gebruiken."

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:384
msgid ""
"Dependent entities — uncheck any to skip generating that category on top of "
"whatever master data ends up present. Applies to every source (procedural, "
"Excel, hybrid)."
msgstr ""
"Afhankelijke entiteiten — vink uit om die categorie niet te genereren "
"bovenop de aanwezige master-data. Geldt voor elke bron (procedureel, Excel, "
"hybride)."

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:388
msgid "Generate activities"
msgstr "Activiteiten genereren"

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:389
msgid ""
"uncheck to skip session/match generation. Attendance is generated alongside; "
"turning this off skips both."
msgstr ""
"uitvinken om training/wedstrijd-generatie over te slaan. Aanwezigheid wordt "
"tegelijk gegenereerd; uitvinken slaat beide over."

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:393
msgid "Generate evaluations"
msgstr "Evaluaties genereren"

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:394
msgid "uncheck to skip evaluation rounds + per-category ratings."
msgstr ""
"uitvinken om evaluatierondes + per-categorie-beoordelingen over te slaan."

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:398
msgid "Generate goals"
msgstr "Doelen genereren"

#: src/Modules/DemoData/Admin/DemoDataPage.php:399
msgid "uncheck to skip per-player development goals."
msgstr "uitvinken om per-speler ontwikkelingsdoelen over te slaan."

