msgid ""
"Sees every team, player, evaluation, activity, goal, and report. Cannot edit "
"anything. Use this for board members, parents who want a peek at progress, "
"or external scouts. The role most admins forget exists."
msgstr ""
"Ziet elke ploeg, speler, evaluatie, activiteit, doel en rapport. Kan niets "
